劳动关系。 二审法院认为，用人单位在劳动者处于孕期、产期、哺乳期时，不得依照《劳动合同法》第四十条、第四十一条的规定解除劳动合同，但劳动者具有该法第三十九规定的情形时，用人单位仍然可以依法解除劳动合同。在试用期内劳动者被证明不具备该项能力的，用人单位有权作出解除劳动关系的决定。 驳回上诉，维持原判。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "198 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452038798"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IhKzC2cKghZE9EAMaCDYyNzMyMzA3IOWgi4MGMAY4TkAacgk0NTIwMzg3OTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1617286076.5188832", "card_id": "Q_422926125", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究生实验室恋情和办公室恋情一样不被提倡吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "同一个实验室谈恋爱合适吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-7623944fd3f5958768eca79b44129143_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "194 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/422926125"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IhKzC2cKghZE9EAMaCDU2MjYyMDQ3IISeuPsFMAE4fEAbcgk0MjI5MjYxMjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1617286076.5193043", "card_id": "Q_448694249", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 400}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "每天只睡三小时能行吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我是高三生，平时学习效率比较低，感觉脑子笨，学数学物理都比不过别人，最后九十天我想逼自己一把，每天只睡三个小时，其他时间用来学习比别人慢的东西，我很害怕，可能是需要勇气，或许也需要你的支持吧，所以才提了这个问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3c031badb03c457030738644e00f97dd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "137 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/448694249"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhKzC2cKghZE9EAMaCDYxOTg4ODU1IKqTpIIGMBM4iQZAHHIJNDQ4Njk0MjQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1617286076.5196817", "card_id": "Q_351666167", "feed_specific": {"answer_count"